title: Newsprint Stocks, Canada Included, at Mills, Owned by Mills for U.S. and Canada
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1918-1937 (2)--Original Data, 1936-1948 (3)--Original, 1937-1956. Data Were Computed By Summing The U.S. And Canada. Beginning In 1936, Data Include Stocks Owned By Mills But Stored In Warehouses. The Newsprint Service Bureau Says It Is Not Possible To Separate Out The Stored-In-Warehouses Figures, As The Mills Submit Only One Figure. Source: The Newsprint Service Bureau And The U.S. Department Of Commerce, Survey Of Current Business

This NBER data series m05034b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 5 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter05.html.
